name: CAROUSEL LOVE LAND
description: Here is the caravan carousel at Disney-Sea, Tokyo. My boy and I went and enjoy together in summer 2019 before Covid-19 situation. Today is the 3rd anniversary day with him, so I created it for cerebrate and let us remember our happiness. I changed and added something special to made it completely likes my feeling at that moment (everything be pink) and want it comes (my dog Choco). Hope you guys can touch. Love
